### Get top 15 cards by current price (highest first)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/price_change/top-bottom?column=current_price&sort=desc

### Get top 15 cards by current price (lowest first)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/price_change/top-bottom?column=current_price&sort=asc

### Get top 15 cards by price change (highest change first)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/price_change/top-bottom?column=price_change&sort=desc

### Get top 15 cards by percentage change (ascending)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/price_change/top-bottom?column=percentage_change&sort=asc

### Default behavior (current_price desc)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/price_change/top-bottom
